.com/niconikon01</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-戒賭熱線-</strong><br />\nTEL: 183 4633<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkjc.com/responsible-gambling/images/footer_icon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fresponsible-gambling%2Fimages%2Ffooter_icon.jpg&h=f8bd194a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚相介紹:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9XvguU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9XvguU.jpg&h=d4003f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n神父靚圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/770riqm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F770riqm.png&h=af9129b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">新手須知</span><br />\n連登apps台既fgo post係主要討論<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日</span></span>ser<br />\n台服問題可免則免<br />\n以下內容只適用於<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日</span></span>ser<br />\n呢隻game三十石=十抽<br />\n課金就650hkd左右=167石<br />\n假如你想長玩 最符合效率就係<br />\n你可以先係淘寶買個首抽ac(顧名思義係全新ac但係有石)<br />\n大概四十蚊到 入面有幾十符+900幾石<br />\n你冇睇錯只係四十蚊港紙左右<br />\n<br />\n刷到有3-4個五星 就可以選擇開局<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>-催post專用環保post-</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1422551/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1422551/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHfGH22.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHfGH22.gif&h=a73d85ce&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"110e992bc9c2983cbbe35acaab1cddc541fde7ac","tid":1988662,"uid":200787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"拎完要升靈基一次再升到絆5先會有,留名睇on9唔記得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3151c64b3fad2faec86a44e469dc1b9bae25fe8a","tid":1988662,"uid":60107,"like":0,"dislike":